<object name="Trigonometry Conversion Operators" page="trigconversion" parent="" type="enhancement" version="Gideros 2017.10"><![CDATA[<br />
Operators to convert from one type of measurement to another.<br /><br />

<b> ^< </b>deg &emsp; Convert 'deg' into radians.<br />
<b> ^> </b>rad &emsp; Convert 'rad' into degrees.<br />
]]>
  <platform>android</platform>
  <platform>ios</platform>
  <platform>mac</platform>
  <platform>pc</platform>
  <example name="Simple ^< examples"><![CDATA[<br /> 
r=^<d -- faster than r=math.rad(d)
radAngle=^<sprite:getRotation()
pi=^<180 -- pi is 3.142 in radians or 180 in degrees
]]></example>
  <example name="Simple ^> examples"><![CDATA[<br /> 
d=^>r -- faster than d=math.deg(r)
sprite:setRotation(^>math.sin(0.5))
]]></example>
</object>
